column5: Has anybody off the OFC been fishing Bay Of Quinte this winter ...heading up this week looking for some Hog Walleye ...C&R Only any info would be great Pm me if you don't wana post thanks Fishmaster
There are some great reports on here.
Looking to Ice Fish ...only have time for 1 trip this winter then the Ice Gear goes away for the season
I've been out quite a few times... send me a PM and I'll fill you in on a few spots with safe ice.
